{"tid":1230253,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果你得一個人猶豫緊去唔去遊行，同我入一入黎","createTime":"2019-06-16T06:54:01.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T11:09:25.000Z","uid":30835,"like":431,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":54,"replies":[{"pid":"86763d1beb00c05c92e32f82507e9820a2270180","tid":1230253,"uid":30835,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:54:01.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">去！一定要去</span></span><br />\n依家全港地鐵個個都係黑衫巴打絲打<br />\n只要你出聲大把巴打陪你<br />\n你再唔出黎就可能以後都再冇機會出黎<br />\n你要記住<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">你並唔係自己一個人，而你全港人一齊陪你</span></span><br />\n我地唔可以比果位烈士巴打白白犧牲<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">香港人加油</span></span>"},{"pid":"63a89acc1aea36a37982d70118679d34fece19bc","tid":1230253,"uid":30835,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:56:08.000Z","msg":"推比更多自己一個猶豫緊既巴絲睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f91f36a19e9c1d804fb4227d0599d48db4374e54","tid":1230253,"uid":229955,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T06:57:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大會宣布 提前出發 @ 14:30 <br />\n<br />\n1) 由維園 去 金鐘添美道<br />\n2) 2 條 BANNER : 「痛心疾首」 「撤回惡法」 由宗教界 同 一班媽媽帶領<br />\n3) 「痛心疾首」 BANNER 會放喺適當地方 , 畀各市民獻花<br />\n4) 有宗教界負責安排 祈禱會<br />\n5) 有支援抗爭者基金籌款箱<br />\n<br />\n616 黑色大遊行 五大宗旨:<br />\n<br />\n1) 撒回惡法<span style=\"font-size: large;\"></span><br />\n2) 釋放被捕既抗爭者<br />\n3) 我們不是暴徒<br />\n4) 追究黑警開槍責任<br />\n5) 淋病下台</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警冷血，林鄭殺港<br />\n無線新聞，出賣港人</span></span><br />\n<br 